headline: Is Quanta Services Still Attractive After 548% Five-Year Surge and Grid Project Wins?
summary: Ever wondered if Quanta Services is a steal at current prices, or if you’re better off waiting for a better entry point? Let’s dig into what’s behind the stock’s impressive run and whether it still has value left for new investors. After an outstanding 548.0% gain over five years and a strong 32.9% climb in the last year, Quanta Services has hit some turbulence recently.
